title: Missing method "SKPath.Contains(x, y)"
body:
The following method is missing on SKPath "SKPath.Contains(x, y)". 

See: `bool SkPath::contains(SkScalar x, SkScalar y) const` https://github.com/google/skia/blob/44df651ebefc284acc2f66425dff3ea0b0e14b36/src/core/SkPath.cpp#L3146
